    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>SPEEDOMETER INPUT FROM ECU</title>
        <para>With the WTEC III transmission, the electronic speedometer and engine ECM receive a data signal over the
            data link from the transmission ECU. The WTEC III ECU receives its signal from the transmission output speed
            sensor.
        </para>
